<title>USA: First Financial names affiliate chairman.</title>
<headline>First Financial names affiliate chairman.</headline>
<dateline>HAMILTON, Ohio 1996-08-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>First Financial Bancorp said on Wednesday it named James Hall the chairman of Fidelity Federal Savings Bank, its affiliate.</p>
<p>The company said it also named Hall the president and chief executive of the bank.</p>
